    <entry>
      <title>01-init</title>
      <link href="/2023/02/25/%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE-%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E5%BA%93/01-init/"/>
      <url>/2023/02/25/%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE-%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E5%BA%93/01-init/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id=""><a href="#" class="headerlink" title=""></a></h2><p>技术选型<br>前端：前端3件套html、css、JavaScript, vue3, Ant Design Vue<br>后端：</p><ul><li>java(8.0)</li><li>spring(DI更好管理项目依赖)</li><li>springmvc(restful编程风格，提供接口访问)</li><li>mybatis(java操作数据库的框架)</li><li>mybatis-plus(mybatis加强版，不用写sql语句就可以增删改查)</li><li>springboot(快速启动项目，集成框架 2.7.10 稳定版本)</li><li>junit(单元测试)</li><li>mysql(关系型数据库，使用8.x版本)</li></ul><h2 id="-1"><a href="#-1" class="headerlink" title=""></a></h2><p>第一天</p><blockquote><p>初始化项目，使用git将代码提交到本地仓库，并提交到gitee(在家里提交到github超时，改用github)<br>controller接口测试 TestController</p></blockquote><h3 id="-2"><a href="#-2" class="headerlink" title=""></a></h3><p>日志优化<br>logback-spring.xml 日志配置文件</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--            &lt;Pattern&gt;%d&#123;yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS&#125; %highlight(%-5level) %blue(%-50logger&#123;50&#125;:%-4line) %thread %green(%-18X&#123;LOG_ID&#125;) %msg%n&lt;/Pattern&gt;--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- 时间 日志类别 所在类 线程 具体信息--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Pattern</span>&gt;</span>%d&#123;ss.SSS&#125; %highlight(%-5level) %blue(%-30logger&#123;30&#125;:%-4line) %thread %green(%-18X&#123;LOG_ID&#125;) %msg%n<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">Pattern</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="-3"><a href="#-3" class="headerlink" title=""></a></h3><p>restful风格</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># controller层类使用<span class="meta">@RestMapping(相当于@Controller + @ResponseBody)</span></span><br><span class="line"># <span class="meta">@Controller</span> 表示controller层</span><br><span class="line"># <span class="meta">@ResponseBody</span> 返回json字符串</span><br><span class="line"># Restful风格 Get Post Put Delete</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@RestController</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">TestController</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@GetMapping(&quot;/hello&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> String <span class="title function_">hello</span><span class="params">()</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">&quot;hello world&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="-4"><a href="#-4" class="headerlink" title=""></a></h3><p>controller层接口测试</p><blockquote><p>使用以.http结尾文件测试<br>例：test.http 用于TestController中&#x2F;hello接口测试</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight http"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># gtr快捷键生成一下两行</span><br><span class="line">GET http://localhost:8880/hello</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">Accept</span><span class="punctuation">: </span>application/json</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&gt; &#123;%</span><br><span class="line">client.test(&quot;test-hello&quot;, function() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  client.log(&quot;测试/hello接口&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">  client.log(response.body);</span><br><span class="line">  client.assert(response.status === 200, &quot;返回码不是200&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">  client.assert(response.body === &quot;hello world&quot;, &quot;结果错误&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"> %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="-5"><a href="#-5" class="headerlink" title=""></a></h3><p>配置文件</p><blockquote><p>在resource中添加config文件夹，新建一份application.yml配置文件用于项目上线使用；在resource下的application.yml用于生产测试使用。<br>当两个配置文件有配置冲突时，config下的配置文件生效</p></blockquote><h2 id="-6"><a href="#-6" class="headerlink" title=""></a></h2><p>解决配置错误小技巧</p><blockquote><p>项目出现配置问题，关闭项目，在文件资源管理器中将.idea文件夹删除，然后重新打开项目<br>.idea放置项目配置</p></blockquote><h2 id="-7"><a href="#-7" class="headerlink" title=""></a></h2><p>git</p><blockquote><p>git add  将新文件提交到暂存区 (git add . 提交所有新文件) idea中文件绿色表示已添加到暂存区，红色未添加<br>git commit 将暂存区中文件提交到本地仓库 可以使用idea右上角的 绿色√ 提交代码到本地仓库<br>git push 提交到远程仓库  可以idea使用右上角 斜右上方箭头 将代码push到远程仓库</p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
      
